  "title": "Accountant",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Handle full set of accounts, including AP, AR, GL, bank reconciliation, and monthly/year-end closing.</li>\n  <li>Prepare and analyze financial reports, balance sheets, and relevant statements.</li>\n  <li>Manage GST filings, corporate tax submissions, and XBRL annual returns.</li>\n  <li>Review and process staff expense claims accurately and on time.</li>\n  <li>Maintain and improve internal controls and accounting procedures.</li>\n  <li>Liaise with auditors, tax agents, and banks for audits and compliance matters.</li>\n  <li>Support budgeting and financial analysis for management decisions.</li>\n  <li>Assist in implementing SAP and improving finance processes.</li>\n  <li>Contribute to ad-hoc finance tasks and cross-department projects.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No. 20C0270</p>",
